Subject: [BIP Draft] Emoji Seed Mnemonics for Deterministic Keys
Body:
Hello all, Iâ€™d like to propose a new informational BIP: Emoji Seed Mnemonics for Deterministic Keys.
This specifies a deterministic mapping between the BIP-39 English wordlist (2048 words) and 2048 unique emoji pairs.

Motivation:
Provides a language-independent, visual mnemonic format.
Improves memorability and cross-lingual usability.
Backwards-compatible: emoji mnemonics map directly to the existing BIP-39 words.

Scope:
No changes to entropy, checksum, or seed derivation.
Adds an optional, standard emoji mapping layer.

Draft available here: https://emojiseed.com/blob/main/docs/bip-emojiseed.rst

Feedback is most welcome.

